# Smart Health Advisory System

This is a React web application for a Smart Health Advisory System, including a symptom checker, health tips, and health tracker.

## Features

- Symptom Checker with basic advice
- Health Tips categorized by Diet, Fitness, and Mental Health
- Health Tracker to record weight and sleep hours locally
- Responsive and clean UI using Tailwind CSS

## Setup & Run

1. Clone the repo  
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/smart-health-advisory.git
   cd smart-health-advisory

